title: Episode #8: Man Stories with Robert Disque
description: Welcome back to another edition of the Art of Manliness podcast. In this week's episode we return to our series called "Man Stories" where we interview a different gentleman every other week and ask him what it means to be a man. This time our guest is Robert Disque from Ogden, UT.
author: contact@artofmanliness.com (The Art of Manliness)
